title: Toronto JS Social - in person(RSVP Link in description!)
details:
Details
-------

Your favorite in-person event is back!

Join us in this chill social event happening on Wednesday, November 15th!

TorontoJS Social is our lightest event where like minds get together, have a snack or drink, and talk Javascript/coding.

Come meet other developers in the area, talk about development and community, make friends, and let's do something away from the screens!

This event is open to all skill levels, and there's no agenda here other than just catching up with other devs in the community and networking!

Hope to see you all there!

Code of conduct is enforced at all TorontoJS events [https://torontojs.com/p/code\_of\_conduct](https://torontojs.com/p/code_of_conduct)

**Attendees must register on Guild** [https://guild.host/events/toronto-js-social-in-27ewzx](https://guild.host/events/toronto-js-social-in-27ewzx) to reserve their spot
